a Mesthri]]'' ||<ref>https://ia600101.us.archive.org/5/items/41stAnnualFilmfareBestTeluguActor/BestTeluguActor.jpg</ref>\n|-\n| 1992 || '''[[Chiranjeevi]]''' ||Madhava|| ''[[Aapathbandavudu]]'' ||<ref>https://ia601501.us.archive.org/17/items/40thFilmfareSouthBestActorActress/40th%20Filmfare%20South%20Best%20Actor%20Actress.jpg</ref><ref>https://ia801500.us.archive.org/7/items/40thFilmfareSouthBestActorActressFilmsLifetimeMusicDirector/40th%20filmfare%20south%20best%20actor%20actress%20films%20lifetime%20music%20director.jpg</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#edf3fe;\"\n| 1991 || '''[[Akkineni Nageswara Rao]]''' ||Sitharamayya|| ''[[Seetharamaiah Gari Manavaralu]]'' ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.is/HxfW9|author=Santosh|title=39th Annual Filmfare Best Actor Director Telugu Winners|publisher=archive.is|date=7 February 2017|accessdate=6 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=x-zeAAAAMAAJ&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=Filmfare+Awards+best+film|title=Sainik Samachar: The Pictorial Weekly of the Armed Forces|date=16 December 1993|publisher=Director of Public Relations, Ministry of Defence|via=Google Books}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1990 || '''[[Rajasekhar (actor)|Rajasekhar]]''' ||Vikram|| ''[[Magaadu (1990 film)|Magaadu]]'' ||<ref>Refer Filmfare Magazine August 1991, [[38th filmfare awards south]] Juhi Chawla Shilpa Abused Madras Awards:Winners</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#edf3fe;\"\n| 1989 || '''[[Kamal Haasan]]''' ||{{*}}G. K. Rayudu<br>{{*}}Chandram|| ''[[Indrudu Chandrudu]]'' ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NB3VAAAAMAAJ&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=Indrudu+Chandrudu|title=India Today|date=16 December 1990|publisher=Living Media India Pvt. Limited|via=Google Books}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1988 || '''[[Daggubati Venkatesh| Venkatesh]]''' || Shakti|| ''[[Brahma Putrudu]]'' || \n|- style=\"background:#edf3fe;\"\n| 1987 || '''[[Akkineni Nageswara Rao]]'''  ||Ananda Rao||  ''[[Aatma Bandhuvulu]]'' ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.is/