ka Srikanth|Srikanth]] \u2013 ''[[Operation Duryodhana (film)|Operation Duryodhana]]''\n**[[Daggubati Venkatesh|Venkatesh]] \u2013 ''[[Aadavari Matalaku Arthale Verule]]''\n**[[Allu Arjun]]-''[[Desamuduru]]''\n*'''2006: [[Mahesh Babu]]''' - '''''[[Pokiri]]'''''\n**[[Siddharth (actor)|Siddharth]] - ''[[Bommarillu]]''\n**[[Akkineni Nagarjuna|Nagarjuna]] - ''[[Sri Ramadasu]]''\n**[[N. T. Rama Rao Jr.|Jr. NTR]] - ''[[Rakhi (2006 film)|Rakhi]]''\n*'''2005: [[Siddharth (actor)|Siddharth]]''' \u2013 '''''[[Nuvvostanante Nenoddantana]]'''''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070429030243/http://www.cinegoer.com/archives/september2006/filmfarewinners.htm|title=CineGoer.com - News (September 2006) - 53rd Annual Filmfare Awards-South Winners|date=29 April 2007|website=web.archive.org}}</ref>\n**[[Daggubati Venkatesh|Venkatesh]] \u2013 ''[[Sankranti (film)|Sankranti]]''\n**[[Akkineni Nagarjuna|Nagarjuna]] \u2013 ''[[Super (2005 film)|Super]]''\n**[[Mahesh Babu]] \u2013 ''[[Athadu]]''\n**[[Prabhas]] \u2013 ''[[Chhatrapati (film)|Chhatrapati]]''\n*'''2004: [[Chiranjeevi]]''' - '''''[[Shankar Dada M.B.B.S.]]'''''\n**[[Rajendra Prasad (actor)|Rajendra Prasad]] - ''[[Aa Naluguru]]''\n** [[Allu Arjun]] - [[Arya (2004 film)|Arya]]\n** [[Akkineni Nagarjuna|Nagarjuna]] - [[Mass (film)|Mass]]\n**[[Prabhas]] - ''[[Varsham (2004 film)|Varsham]]''\n*'''2003: [[Mahesh Babu]]''' - '''''[[Okkadu]]'''''\n**[[Mahesh Babu]] - ''[[Nijam]]''\n**[[N. T. Rama Rao Jr.|Jr. NTR]] - ''[[Simhadri (2003 film)|Simhadri]]''\n**[[Chiranjeevi]] - ''[[Tagore (film)|Tagore]]''\n*'''2002: [[Chiranjeevi]]''' - '''''[[Indra (2002 film)|Indra]]'''''\n**[[Uday Kiran]] - ''[[Nee Sneham]]''\n**[[N. T. Rama Rao Jr.|Jr. NTR]] - ''[[Aadi (2002 film)|Aadi]]''\n** [[Akkineni Nagarjuna|Nagarjuna]] - ''[[Santosham (2002 film)|Santosham]]''\n*'''2001: [[Uday Kiran]]''' - '''''[[Nuvvu Nenu]]'''''<ref>{{cite news|url=http://downloads.movies.indiatimes.com/south2001/tel_nom.html|work=The Times Of India|title=49th An